{"tid":2408056,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"美國國會就 GME 事件舉行聽證會　Robinhood 及 Reddit 總裁將出席","createTime":"2021-02-14T14:46:06.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-14T18:22:44.000Z","uid":66271,"like":12,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"6f603bc860df3fe04c13df69af6cf7bc0cf86146","tid":2408056,"uid":66271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-14T14:46:06.000Z","msg":"一月尾的時候 GameStop 事件成為了美國金融界一大新聞，同時也令人關注金融體系可能出現的漏洞。最近美國國會就舉行聽證會，Robinhood 和 Reddit 的總裁都將會出席。<br />\n<br />\n美國國會金融服務委員會在 2 月 18 日將會舉行一場視像聽證會，希望可以對 GameStop 股價暴增然後暴跌的事件進行更深入調查，其中傳召的證人包括投資平台 Robinhood 的總裁 Vlad Tenev、網上論壇 Reddit 的總裁 Steve Huffman 以及 YouTuber Keith Gill。<br />\n<br />\nKeith Gill 本身在 Reddit 和 Twitter 上一直有對 GameStop 的股價作評論，也被認為是今次事件的始作俑者之一。而 Robinhood 就作為美國極受散戶歡迎的投資平台，亦可說是今次散戶大舉入市的推手，不過後來由於限制購入 GameStop 股票因此招來抨擊。這次聽證會屆時將會在網上直播，有興趣的朋友不妨留意。"},{"pid":"299f1678da28bf8502ecf9f31c0f2a763cacaa28","tid":2408056,"uid":347528,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-14T14:47:32.000Z","msg":"robinhood搞走曬啲人<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a3a696f8630f0cc4e54cae7b7e6db19ca7d9e5cc","tid":2408056,"uid":36820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-14T14:49:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/peanut.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"22e90b9597c903059b815cbff2f53342e1d2d454","tid":2408056,"uid":246968,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-14T14:51:03.000Z","msg":"期待"},{"pid":"43514e0e270f338c6bfb252a73c6b68cdefcf767","tid":2408056,"uid":35408,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-14T14:59:47.000Z","msg":"攪嚟又點<br />\n個價唔會上啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e21cdbd2d34177f67ff5e496d7723a114122e17","tid":2408056,"uid":390773,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-14T15:09:54.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"3591722baedd02